Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.34,0:00:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(182,348)\fnImpact\fax-0.5\fscy200\fscx150\fs38\shad0\1c&H2A298D&\3c&HC0C0C0&\3a&HD0&\b1}Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up! Set Up! Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gin no kamen ni kuro mafuraa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A mask of silver and a black muffler
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.99,0:00:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hitai ni kagayaku Bui to Bui
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.99,0:00:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,V and V shining on his forehead
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Sutoppu! Goddo no waru-dakumi」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stop GOD's conspiracy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.96,0:00:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no sakebi wa nami no oto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.96,0:00:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,His father's scream is the sound of the waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.76,0:00:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ikari no Raidoru hikinuite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.76,0:00:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Furiously drawing the Ridol
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa kyou mo yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider comes again today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.95,0:00:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X! X! X!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Killed with his father by the evil organisation GOD,\NJin Keisuke is revived as Kamen Rider X.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,His mission: to preserve peace and justice by\Nfighting the mysterious agency known as GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Geist's Mad Bug Hell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.60,0:01:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to have\Ndone!? Let me go! Spare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.80,0:01:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Geist! Thank goodness\Nyou're here! Tell them to stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:01:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I revived that legendary Ancient\NGreek insect for GOD's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.70,0:02:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Please spare me! Why don't you\Nsay something, Apollo Geist?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.20,0:02:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Aota, GOD no longer needs you.\NAs such, you're to be disposed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be so ruthless!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.90,0:02:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The legendary insect of Ancient Greece\Nwhich you revived: the Mad Bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.90,0:02:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only fitting that the discoverer\Nexperience its horrifying effect himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.30,0:02:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,S-stop! Please stop!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.50,0:02:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Bite!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.30,0:03:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an invincible warrior! An immortal warrior!\NKill! I must kill, kill, and kill again!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.20,0:03:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. All humans are your enemy!\NTo battle, warrior of Ancient Greece!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.60,0:03:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Geist.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.50,0:03:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Supreme Commander. The fossil of a Mad Bug has\Nbeen successfully revived in the twentieth century!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.30,0:04:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's said that Ancient Greek soldiers allowed the insect\Nto bite them that they might overcome fear in war.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If they cause humans to hate and kill one\Nanother, these insects will be a boon to GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree. And its reproductive rate\Nis incredible; on par with a cockroach.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If they infest Japan, they'll\Ndrive the people insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let us call it the Insane Japan Plan.\NApollo Geist, I probably don't need to tell you, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.50,0:04:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood. I won't allow the X Rider to interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.40,0:04:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm praying for your success.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.80,0:04:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Incoming report for the Chief of Secret Police:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.20,0:04:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Aota strangled taxi driver to death, now\Ndriving recklessly towards Kotsuyama Apartments.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.10,0:04:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Like clockwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.50,0:04:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:04:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, cross carefully!\NCareful now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.70,0:05:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill... All humans are my enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.50,0:05:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.30,0:05:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That taxi's out\Nof control! Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.70,0:05:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.60,0:05:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness you're alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Pull over!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.10,0:05:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he trying to kill me too!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.70,0:05:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.50,0:05:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing!? Pull over!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better explain yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All humans are my enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.90,0:05:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he really insane?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.40,0:05:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't overstep your position!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't we silence Aota before\NJin Keisuke learns his secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.00,0:06:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! If you kill Aota now, Jin Keisuke\Nwill know it was GOD's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.50,0:06:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Aota must die 'naturally.' Then Jin Keisuke won't\Nsuspect a thing about the Insane Japan Plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you injured?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.80,0:06:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.80,0:06:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We heard about the incident\Nfrom the crossing guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.60,0:06:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. He needs treatment, at any rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.80,0:06:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems something's wrong with his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll call the police once we get him to hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder Apollo Geist is the\NChief of GOD's Secret Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.00,0:07:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't take any chances!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Our secret will be safe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.40,0:07:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... I doubt he's that smart, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.40,0:07:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought your timing was too good to be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now talk! What's GOD want with this man!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.80,0:07:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.50,0:08:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone wanted to keep his cohort quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.00,0:08:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If he regains consciousness, he\Nmight tell me what GOD are up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're quite something, Jin Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.50,0:08:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Compliments don't seem\Nright coming from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.60,0:08:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But thanks to GOD, especially you,\NI can't just trust other people anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So, are you planning to\Ntake that man with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.00,0:08:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let me warn you he's\Nno longer of any use to GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.20,0:08:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you still take him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.00,0:08:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd still be myself, even without GOD!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I ignore a dying\Nman right in front of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.30,0:08:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And you'll fight for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.20,0:08:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.80,0:08:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke! Apollo Geist isn't just\Nthe Chief of GOD's Secret Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.40,0:08:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He's also known as GOD's Killing Machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.50,0:08:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.90,0:09:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.60,0:09:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Change!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.00,0:09:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Try this! Apollo Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.90,0:10:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You coward! Is this how you\Nfight a duel, Apollo Geist?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.90,0:10:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You've only just realised?\NHow naive you are, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.90,0:10:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.20,0:10:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,X Kic--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.60,0:10:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The X Rider's finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.10,0:11:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Dolt! The X Rider went in\Nvoluntarily. He's just buying time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.70,0:11:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll show himself again\Nwhen he sees an opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What a dreadful foe...\NKilling Aota right before my eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That was my chance to defeat Apollo Geist...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what are GOD after, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.80,0:11:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,One Mad Bug can breed\Nthis much in half a day?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Its reproductive powers\Nare greater than I'd thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.60,0:12:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this one to the next target location.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you--\NSir! Your change, your change!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.00,0:12:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What a weird customer...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.80,0:12:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck happened here!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.60,0:13:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster cockroach!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.30,0:13:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.30,0:13:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people died in the coffee shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.60,0:13:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,People died...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.00,0:13:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The police are holding the manager as a suspect!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.80,0:13:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The police?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.80,0:13:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You can't just arrest me without\Ninvestigating! Is this police procedure!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.60,0:13:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No Tokyo police station is\Nholding the chief. So where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is anyone there? I can prove\NI'm innocent! Call Jin Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.80,0:14:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Geist!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.20,0:14:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Officer, arrest this man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.60,0:14:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a member of this secret organisation called\NGOD! He's an evil thug with his eyes on Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.40,0:14:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no time to laugh!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.80,0:14:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How dense you are.\NHaven't you realised it yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.20,0:14:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Tokyo branch of GOD's\NSecret Police! We police the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.40,0:14:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was a trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.60,0:14:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Tachibana... We will call\NJin Keisuke, as you requested.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.60,0:14:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have a couple of\Nquestions for you first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.80,0:14:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Does GOD's Secret Police honour\Nmy right to remain silent?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.00,0:14:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We do, but... I wonder\Nhow long you'll last?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.80,0:15:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Torturing me won't help!\NI won't tell you anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.70,0:15:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see how Tachibana likes pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.90,0:15:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Curses, where's the Mad Bug gone?\NApollo Geist will punish me if I don't find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.40,0:15:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...It might even mean execution!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you're looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.40,0:15:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A paleobiology expert told me about Greece's\Nlegendary Mad Bug, extinct for two thousand years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.20,0:15:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That explains the runaway taxi,\Nand the murders that happened here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk!! Where is GOD\Nbreeding the Mad Bugs!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.80,0:16:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Please, don't do it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.20,0:16:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't if you talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.00,0:16:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! The Tokyo branch\Nof GOD's Secret Police...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.30,0:16:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Tachibana must be there too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.90,0:16:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Awake, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.40,0:16:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We've plenty of time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.70,0:16:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's against my principles to rush things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,One of those bugs was in my shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.80,0:16:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And you've seen what they can do.\NTheir bite turns humans into killing machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How would you like to live as a killing machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no antidote for the Mad Bug's venom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.10,0:17:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Or you could just answer my questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not difficult...\NWill you listen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.30,0:17:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What if you could never live as a normal\Nhuman again... Never see Jin Keisuke again...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But realise your dream of\Nbecoming a grand prix racer?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.30,0:17:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It can stay a dream! I'd rather die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.50,0:17:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill me! You won't make me talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.00,0:17:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have your wish! Die in\Nmadness, Tachibana Toubei!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke, the rest is up to you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.80,0:17:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be long now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.60,0:17:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ridol Rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:18:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.00,0:18:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider, you're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.20,0:18:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.40,0:18:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you find this place!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,One of your own men told me all\Nabout those horrible Mad Bugs!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.90,0:18:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That idiot...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.00,0:18:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider, I can't let you leave the Tokyo\Nbranch of GOD's Secret Police alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.50,0:18:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the X Rider will destroy your Tokyo branch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.70,0:18:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Change!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.00,0:18:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.20,0:18:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wipe out the Mad Bugs!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.00,0:18:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:19:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mad Bugs...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's on fire!\NX Rider...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Tokyo branch\Nis burning! C'mon, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.10,0:19:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it! That X Rider...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.40,0:19:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.40,0:19:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.20,0:20:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Geist Cutter!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.80,0:21:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,X Fatal Kick!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.30,0:21:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the end of Apollo Geist?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.00,0:21:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider... I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.50,0:21:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You were... a good rival,\Nand a worthy opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.80,0:21:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,One last handshake...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.30,0:22:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Geist, it's a shame\Nwe had to be enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.00,0:22:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.30,0:22:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Take my Arm Bomb and die with me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.80,0:22:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn! It won't come off!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.90,0:22:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider! X Rider...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.60,0:22:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.10,0:22:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're alright!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.50,0:22:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.60,0:22:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Geist's timing was just a\Nlittle off because of his injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.30,0:22:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He might have been my enemy,\Nbut I have to respect how he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.20,0:23:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Geist of GOD's Secret Police is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.60,0:23:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But no sooner has the X Rider overcome one crisis\Nthan GOD's demonic hands reach for him again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.17,0:23:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(462,470)\fad(0,850)\fs38}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.18,0:23:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(194,72)\fs38}Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.20,0:23:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Two students are chased by a strange man, but\NJin Keisuke saves them from the Death God Kronos.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.10,0:23:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke infiltrates GOD's fortress, the Palace of Apollon. But what is this Palace of Apollon?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.90,0:23:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode:\N"GOD's Secret Base! X Rider Sneaks in!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.16,0:23:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.16,0:23:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X, X Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.76,0:23:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no tsukutta Kaizoogu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.76,0:23:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kaizorg created by my father
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.66,0:23:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tetsu yori tsuyoi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.66,0:23:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Stronger than iron
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.73,0:23:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oto yori hayai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.73,0:23:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster than sound
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.86,0:23:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu masuku paafekutaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.86,0:23:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,X's mask, Perfecter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.73,0:23:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no negai ga ore no chi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.73,0:23:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My father's wishes are in my blood
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.11,0:24:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Warui yatsura ni makeru na to」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.11,0:24:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't lose to those villains!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.35,0:24:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sakende iru ze
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.35,0:24:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He screams
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.44,0:24:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Itsu made mo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.44,0:24:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Eternally
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.62,0:24:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.62,0:24:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.68,0:24:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.68,0:24:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider